headline: Atlanta University Center Consortium and Mastercard Partner to Launch 2025 Data Challenge Empowering HBCU Students to Drive Inclusive Growth
summary: The Atlanta University Center Consortium (AUCC) Data Science Initiative (DSI) has partnered with the Mastercard Center for Inclusive Growth to launch the 2025 Mastercard Data Challenge, a nationwide competition that empowers HBCU students to use data science for social good.
